      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for computational validation using blood analogue fluid.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments use water-glycerol blood analogue; biological sample variability is not applicable to this fluid system. MRL 2 does not require formal test sample characterization for non-biological working fluids in hemolysis analogue studies."
    },
    {
