    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to gradation 1 per MRL 2 table. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 at all five operating points with conservative model bias. The uncertainty quantification campaign, including Sobol sensitivity indices and parametric envelopes documented in the validation report, supports confidence in model predictions across the COU operating envelope. Decision consequence is HIGH but model influence is MEDIUM; testing confirmation pathway is available. Credibility assessment team unanimously recommends acceptance for regulatory submission.",
